<div class="space-y-2 my-12">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-2">Hey, I'm Mahad! ðŸ‘‹</h1>
  <p>Nice to meet you! I'm a 17-year-old software engineer based in the UK.</p>
